com.elvenrings.qdemo.interfaces

Interface Questionable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FillBlankQuestion, MultipleChoiceQuestion, SingleChoiceQuestion

    public interface Questionable
    Question classes that implement this interface can rendered/displayed by a Renderer object. For now renderers supported are Console and Swing Renderers. HTML and XML renderers are on the TODO list.
    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Iliasu Salifu, iliasu@elvenrings.com
